{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":350100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3501_00_01","textHome":"给神滨市的大家都带来幸福这种事……我真的@能做到吗？一个人确实有点难呦？但是由我@和怜一起做的话，不就什么都能解决了嘛？@和梨花一起……嗯。对啊……和梨花一起的@话……什么都能做到。"}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":350100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3501_00_17","textHome":"虽然我不太会滑雪……但很喜欢坐雪橇……怜@坐在雪橇上的样子……哼哼，想象起来还真@可爱呐！"}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":350100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3501_00_18","textHome":"下次一起去坐雪橇吧！找个滑雪场就行！嗯…@…很期待！……雪啊，快点积起来吧……"}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":350100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3501_00_19","textHome":"步调很一致呢！说不定下次还能打出更强的魔@法！"}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":350100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3501_00_20","textHome":"就像在新降的雪里留下足迹那样……现在的我@，心脏在悸动……嗯！"}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":350100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3501_00_21","textHome":"哦哦？又不谋而合了呢！我们的成长潜力不是@挺惊人嘛？嗯！我们……还可以变得更强…@…我有这种感觉！"}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":350100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3501_00_22","textHome":"多亏有梨花在……感觉我比以前……变得更强@了……不是哦，怜是努力的孩子，是靠自己@变强的哦。努力下去的勇气……是梨花给我@的……谢谢你……"}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":350100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3501_00_23","textHome":"明年的圣诞节，也要让大伙幸福！下一个目标@是全世界！明年……也可以吗？和我一起…@…嗯！和怜在一起才做得到嘛！"}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":350101,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3501_01_24","textHome":"哦——来了来了。怜还没到哦。她忘了东西所@以先回家去取了。就先来和我一块吃点东西@吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":350101}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"id":350101,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"id":350101,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":350101}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":350101,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3501_01_25","textHome":"早耶！虽然我并不擅长早起，但这么盛大的节@日，可是一大早就心情MAX的哦！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":350101,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"id":350101,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":350101,"motion":100}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":350101,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3501_01_26","textHome":"今天午饭吃什么？既然是圣诞节……烤鸡？还@是披萨？奶油炖汤？只要是妈妈做的东西，@我都很喜欢！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":350101,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":350101}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":350101,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":350101,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":350101}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":350100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3501_00_02","textHome":"圣诞快乐！为神滨的大家带来幸福的魔法少女@，绫野梨花还有 五十铃怜……请多关照…@…嗯。"}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":350101,"motion":201,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3501_01_27","textHome":"呜～好冷！到了这个时间，虽然天还亮着，但@已经冷起来了……回去路上要不去哪里坐坐@？暖和一下身子也好！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":350101}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"id":350101,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"eyeC